@startuml TestHaters_ctflow

actor User
participant "VS Code" as VSCode
participant "CTFLOW Extension" as Extension
participant "Webview UI" as WebviewUI
participant "Compiler" as Compiler
participant "Cypress" as Cypress
database "Firebase" as Firebase

User -> VSCode : Open VS Code
VSCode -> Extension : Load CTFLOW extension
Extension -> WebviewUI : Initialize React-based UI
User -> WebviewUI : Interact with drag-and-drop interface
WebviewUI -> WebviewUI : Update visual test flow
WebviewUI -> Firebase : Sync changes (if collaborative)
User -> WebviewUI : Request test compilation
WebviewUI -> Compiler : Send test flow data
Compiler -> Compiler : Generate Cypress code
Compiler -> Extension : Return generated code
Extension -> VSCode : Create/update .cy.js file
User -> Extension : Execute test
Extension -> Cypress : Run generated test
Cypress -> Extension : Return test results
Extension -> WebviewUI : Display test results
WebviewUI -> User : Show test outcome

@enduml